	<h3 align = "center"> Frequently Asked Questions </h3>
	
	
	<p>
		<b> How do I create an account? </b>
		To create an account, visit our web site and click on the "Register" button.
		You'll need to provide your personal information, such as your name, email address, and contact details.
		Follow the instructions to complete the registration process.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> How can I book an appointment with a doctor or specialist? </b>
		After logging into your account, use the search feature to find a doctor or specialist.
		Once you've found the right health care provider, select an available time slot, and follow the 
		steps to book your appointment.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> What information do I need to provide when booking an appointment? </b>
		Typically, you'll need to provide your personal details, the reason for your visit,
		and your preferred date and time for the appointment.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> Can I change or cancel an appointment I've already booked? </b>
		Yes, you can change or cancel your appointment by logging into your account and accessing the 
		appointment details. Be sure to check our cancellation and rescheduling policies for any associated 
		fees or time restrictions.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> What payment methods are accepted for appointment bookings? </b>
		We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards, online payment services, and 
		other options. Payment details will be provided during the booking process.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> How do I search for specific doctors or specialists in my area? </b>
		Use the search bar on our platform to enter the doctor's name, specialty, or location.
		You can filter search results by various criteria to find the right health care provider.
	</p>
		
	<p>
		<b> Can I review the qualifications and experience of the doctors on the platform? </b>
		Yes, you can view detailed profiles of doctors and specialists, including their qualifications,
		experience, patient reviews, and areas of expertise.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> Is my personal and medical information secure on this platform? </b>
		We prioritize the security and privacy of your information.
		Our platform employs encryption and follows strict privacy policies to safeguard your data.
		Please review our privacy policy for more details.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> What should I do if I experience technical issues while using the platform? </b>
		Contact our customer support team for assistance with technical issues. We're here to help resolve 
		any problems you encounter.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> Can I receive appointment reminders via email or SMS? </b>
		Yes, we offer appointment reminders via email or SMS to help you stay organized and ensure you 
		don't miss your appointments.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> What is the policy for refunds if I need to cancel my appointment? </b>
		Refund policies vary, and some appointments may be non-refundable.
		Please review our cancellation and refund policy for specific details.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		<b> How do I provide feedback or report issues with my appointment experience? </b>
		You can provide feedback through our platform or contact our customer support team to report any 
		issues or share your experience.
	</p>
	
	

